ode_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "open", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2023-03-10T15:13:49Z", "updated_at": "2023-04-05T17:25:36Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "<!--\r\nThank you for filing a bug report! \ud83d\udc1b Please provide a short summary of the bug,\r\nalong with any information you feel relevant to replicating the bug.\r\n-->\r\n\r\nI tried this code:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\n#![no_std]\r\n\r\npub trait Foo {\r\n    fn do_thing(&self) -> u32;\r\n}\r\npub struct A {}\r\n\r\nimpl Foo for A {\r\n    fn do_thing(&self) -> u32 {\r\n       0\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n#[inline(never)]\r\npub fn tst(arg : &dyn Foo) -> u32 {\r\n    arg.do_thing()\r\n}\r\n\r\npub fn with_a(an_a : &A) -> u32 {\r\n    tst(an_a)\r\n}\r\n\r\n```\r\nA compiler explorer link for convenience:\r\n\r\nhttps://godbolt.org/z/d5bzqWrMW\r\n\r\nI expected to see this happen: `tst` should use a position relative sequence to load the function pointer from the table.\r\n\r\nInstead, this happened:\r\n\r\n```\r\njmp     qword ptr [rsi + 24]\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhich requires the entry to be an absolute address.\r\n\r\n### Meta\r\n<!--\r\nIf you're using the stable version of the compiler, you should also check if the\r\nbug also exists in the beta or nightly versions.\r\n-->\r\n\r\nTried on 1.67 and nightly. Also tried for RISCV64 which had the same problem. \r\n\r\nThe compiler flags I passed:\r\n\r\n```\r\n-C opt-level=2 -C  relocation-model=pie -C link-arg=--no-dynamic-linker\r\n```\r\n\r\n`-C link-arg=--no-dynamic-linker` does not actually change anything.\r\n\r\n<!--\r\nInclude a backtrace in the code block by setting `RUST_BACKTRACE=1` in your\r\nenvironment. E.g. `RUST_BACKTRACE=1 cargo build`.\r\n-->\r\n<details><summary>Backtrace</summary>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\n```\r\n<backtrace>\r\n```\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n</details>\r\n", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/108985/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/108985/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}